professional_summary: Experienced Database Analyst with expertise in SQL Server Administration, Data Extraction, Transformation, and Loading. Skilled in performance tuning, high availability clustering, and data mart design.

key_responsibilities: Developed and maintained SQL Server databases for various projects.
Managed database users and security settings.
Created DTS packages for data extraction and transformation.
Performed performance tuning and query optimization.
Designed and implemented data marts and cubes.
Generated reports using Microsoft Reporting Services.
Provided training and consultation to application development teams.
Configured failover clustering for high availability.
Created and managed database users and login IDs.
Designed cubes and data marts for business needs.
Trained new hires on database administration.
Coordinated technology and employment equity initiatives.
Performed integration testing and resolved issues.
